    "description": "<i><strong>'roll'</strong> is a simple meditative 2D endless runner. As an entity of light, explore an infinitely expanding and eroding scape of light and colour as you calm your mind and body. Uncover unique spaces and hidden secrets while collecting Stars to slowly unravel the stories that both surround the world, as well as yourself.</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065260/extras/d284ab980088ab0ce73628ccf71aac17.poster.avif?t=1722564083\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065260/extras/d284ab980088ab0ce73628ccf71aac17.webm?t=1722564083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>Relax Your Way</strong><br>From the easy gameplay to the calming visuals and gentle soundscapes, relaxation is key. Play a few shorts run to journey a far as possible while a wall of shadows pursues you to aim for a high-score, or disable the shadows to explore the infinite world at your own pace. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065260/extras/ec6254ac33bafcf8c4846e8812507a01.poster.avif?t=1722564083\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065260/extras/ec6254ac33bafcf8c4846e8812507a01.webm?t=1722564083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>Infinite Journeys</strong><br>Every world is created uniquely; the regions, weather, secrets, and even the music itself is designed and arranged while you play. Want to revisit, or even share a world? Simply load a world's <i>Seed</i> to regrow it and return.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065260/extras/d541bb2d0c38f80248bf1fa3b2f9ee3f.poster.avif?t=1722564083\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065260/extras/d541bb2d0c38f80248bf1fa3b2f9ee3f.webm?t=1722564083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>Collectible Lore</strong><br>Across your journeys you will uncover <i>Stars</i>, stories in the form of beautifully drawn cards. Each <i>Star</i> not only provides you strength, but weaves deep tales from passages of introspection to interconnected legends.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065260/extras/225cd3bdc7f6aa521dc46dbe2d542da6.poster.avif?t=1722564083\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065260/extras/225cd3bdc7f6aa521dc46dbe2d542da6.webm?t=1722564083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>Cultivate Yourself</strong><br>After your journeys, you may invest collected <i>Shards</i> into improving your abilities. Instead of having to save for the <i>&quot;next unlock&quot;</i>, any amount of <i>Shards</i> spent provides an increase to your capabilities, allowing you to continue to grow so you can explore faster.<br><br><br><i>Disclaimer: 'roll' has been ported from mobile. It has been updated with unique control schemes and higher-quality graphical rendering, but still maintains simple gameplay and some mid-scale texturing.</i>",
